      <div class="title">        <div class="title-component">     <h2 class="h2 text-left                                  bold-title">         888poker Club User Guide     </h2> </div> </div>                 <div class="rich-text">            <div class="rich-text-component">     <div class="text"><p>Welcome to our 888poker Club User Guide. Here you’ll find everything you need to know about navigating the Club in a few easy steps. Ready to hit the Club? Let’s go!</p></div> </div></div>   </div>                  </div>                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="sidebar">            <div class="sidebar-component">       </div></div>   </div>                  </div>             </div>                                        </div></div> <div class="progressive-number">         <div class="progressive-number-component false">     <div class="number">1</div> </div> </div> <div class="grid"><div class="grid-component">                                                      <div class="column-container  two-columns-50">                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="image">           <div class="image-component img-100">       <div class="image-container js-modal-open modal-enabled">                               <picture>                  <img src="/assets/600x724-Image1-1459323793824_20(1).png" width="600" height="724" alt="How to view your 888poker Club account" loading="lazy">     </picture>       </div>                        <div class="modal js-modal js-modal-close">                <div class="modal-dialog">                     <div class="modal-content js-modal-content">                          <button class="button-close js-modal-button" title="Close (Esc)" aria-label="Close (Esc)">×</button>                                              <picture>                  <img class="modal-image js-modal-image" src="/assets/600x724-Image1-1459323793824_20(1).png" width="600" height="724" alt="How to view your 888poker Club account" loading="lazy">     </picture>                      </div>                </div>           </div>       </div> </div>   </div>                  </div>                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="rich-text">            <div class="rich-text-component">     <div class="text"><h4><b>How to view your 888poker Club account</b></h4> <p>To view a&nbsp;quick summary&nbsp;of your 888poker Club account, just click on the&nbsp;<img src="/assets/SmallLogo-1459673098445.png">&nbsp;button in the 888poker lobby. A pop up window will appear with details on your progress.</p></div> </div></div>                 <div class="rich-text">            <div class="rich-text-component">     <div class="text"><p>To view&nbsp;<b>full details</b>&nbsp;of your 888poker Club account, you can either:</p> <p><b>A)</b>&nbsp;Click on ‘poker club page’ at the bottom right hand corner of the pop up window.</p> <p><b>B)</b>&nbsp;Click on the ‘My 888poker Club’ option, under the ‘My profile’ tab</p></div> </div></div>   </div>                  </div>             </div>                              </div></div> <div class="progressive-number">         <div class="progressive-number-component false">     <div class="number">2</div> </div> </div> <div class="grid"><div class="grid-component">                                                      <div class="column-container  two-columns-50">                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="image">           <div class="image-component img-100">       <div class="image-container js-modal-open modal-enabled">                               <picture>                  <img src="/assets/600x338-Image2-1459323839012.jpg" width="600" height="338" alt="How to view your 888poker Club status" loading="lazy">     </picture>       </div>                        <div class="modal js-modal js-modal-close">                <div class="modal-dialog">                     <div class="modal-content js-modal-content">                          <button class="button-close js-modal-button" title="Close (Esc)" aria-label="Close (Esc)">×</button>                                              <picture>                  <img class="modal-image js-modal-image" src="/assets/600x338-Image2-1459323839012.jpg" width="600" height="338" alt="How to view your 888poker Club status" loading="lazy">     </picture>                      </div>                </div>           </div>       </div> </div>   </div>                  </div>                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="rich-text">            <div class="rich-text-component">     <div class="text"><h3>How to view your 888poker Club status</h3> <p>Once you’ve entered ‘My 888poker Club’, here’s what you’ll see:</p> <p><b>A)</b>&nbsp;Your current Level at the top of the screen.</p> <p><b>B)</b>&nbsp;A progress bar which indicates how many points you’ve already accumulated at this level and how many points you need to reach the next level.</p> <p><b>C)&nbsp;</b>The amount of Gold Tokens waiting for you at the end of this Level.</p> <p><b>D)</b>&nbsp;Your current Gold Token balance.</p></div> </div></div>   </div>                  </div>             </div>                              </div></div> <div class="progressive-number">         <div class="progressive-number-component false">     <div class="number">3</div> </div> </div> <div class="grid"><div class="grid-component">                                                      <div class="column-container  two-columns-50">                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="image">           <div class="image-component img-100">       <div class="image-container js-modal-open modal-enabled">                               <picture>                  <img src="/assets/647x973-Image3-1459323864764.jpg" width="647" height="673" alt="How to take on Challenges" loading="lazy">     </picture>       </div>                        <div class="modal js-modal js-modal-close">                <div class="modal-dialog">                     <div class="modal-content js-modal-content">                          <button class="button-close js-modal-button" title="Close (Esc)" aria-label="Close (Esc)">×</button>                                              <picture>                  <img class="modal-image js-modal-image" src="/assets/647x973-Image3-1459323864764.jpg" width="647" height="673" alt="How to take on Challenges" loading="lazy">     </picture>                      </div>                </div>           </div>       </div> </div>   </div>                  </div>                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="rich-text">            <div class="rich-text-component">     <div class="text"><h4><b>How to take on Challenges</b></h4> <p>You’ll be able to view all your available Challenges on your ‘Challenges’ tab in your account underneath the Progress Bar. Some Challenges will grant points in real time, whereas some will only be updated within 72 hours of the Challenge being completed. All of the Challenges are activated automatically, which means you won’t need to take any action or ‘opt in’ to get started. For example: You’ll start earning points for the ‘Play Poker’ Challenge automatically once you start playing 888poker tournaments or cash games. The buttons to the right of each challenge will take you to the correct place to start completing the Challenge. Additional Challenges may be added to this page from time to time, so keep your eye on the Club!</p></div> </div></div>   </div>                  </div>             </div>                              </div></div> <div class="progressive-number">         <div class="progressive-number-component false">     <div class="number">4</div> </div> </div> <div class="grid"><div class="grid-component">                                                      <div class="column-container  two-columns-50">                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="image">           <div class="image-component img-100">       <div class="image-container js-modal-open modal-enabled">                               <picture>                  <img src="/assets/600x1275-Image4-1459323898471.png" width="600" height="1275" alt="How to view your current Challenge status" loading="lazy">     </picture>       </div>                        <div class="modal js-modal js-modal-close">                <div class="modal-dialog">                     <div class="modal-content js-modal-content">                          <button class="button-close js-modal-button" title="Close (Esc)" aria-label="Close (Esc)">×</button>                                              <picture>                  <img class="modal-image js-modal-image" src="/assets/600x1275-Image4-1459323898471.png" width="600" height="1275" alt="How to view your current Challenge status" loading="lazy">     </picture>                      </div>                </div>           </div>       </div> </div>   </div>                  </div>                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="rich-text">            <div class="rich-text-component">     <div class="text"><div><h4><b>How to view your current Challenge status</b></h4> <p>When a Challenge is active, you’ll be able to view your progress near the Challenge description.<br> <br> When a Challenge is finished or its status changes, a coloured ribbon will appear next to it along with one of the following terms to indicate its status.<br> </p> <p class="colorfull">&nbsp;</p> <p><span style="color: rgb(31,203,62);">Completed:</span> This means you have successfully completed this Challenge and have collected all the points you can possibly get from completing it. A green ribbon will appear on this Challenge.</p> <p><span style="color: rgb(112,168,191);">Expired:</span>This means this Challenge has expired and you can no longer earn points from completing it. A grey ribbon will appear on this Challenge.</p> <p><span style="color: rgb(255,187,0);">Processing Status:</span> This means that we are in the process of calculating whether this Challenge has been successfully completed or if it has expired.</p> <br> <br> <br> <br> <p>When you ‘Level up’ or complete a challenge whilst playing poker, a pop up will appear at the top of the screen to congratulate you.</p> </div></div> </div></div>   </div>                  </div>             </div>                              </div></div> <div class="progressive-number">         <div class="progressive-number-component false">     <div class="number">5</div> </div> </div> <div class="grid"><div class="grid-component">                                                      <div class="column-container  two-columns-50">                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="image">           <div class="image-component img-100">       <div class="image-container js-modal-open modal-enabled">                               <picture>                  <img src="/assets/600x1140-Image5-1459323926773.png" width="600" height="1140" alt="How to redeem your Gold Tokens for prizes" loading="lazy">     </picture>       </div>                        <div class="modal js-modal js-modal-close">                <div class="modal-dialog">                     <div class="modal-content js-modal-content">                          <button class="button-close js-modal-button" title="Close (Esc)" aria-label="Close (Esc)">×</button>                                              <picture>                  <img class="modal-image js-modal-image" src="/assets/600x1140-Image5-1459323926773.png" width="600" height="1140" alt="How to redeem your Gold Tokens for prizes" loading="lazy">     </picture>                      </div>                </div>           </div>       </div> </div>   </div>                  </div>                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="rich-text">            <div class="rich-text-component">     <div class="text"><h4><b>How to redeem your Gold Tokens for prizes</b></h4> <p>Redeeming your Gold Tokens for prizes and bonuses is easy! Just click on the ‘My Gold Tokens’ option, under the ‘My profile’ tab. Alternatively, you can click on the ‘Redeem’ tab at the top of your 888poker club account screen, which will direct you straight to the Redeem Page.<br> <br> Now it’s time to pick your prize! Just choose from the list of bonuses on the Redeem Page.<br> <br> The number of Gold Tokens required for each prize is listed on the right hand side. If an item appears in grey with a ‘locked’ icon on its right, this means you don’t currently have enough Gold Tokens to redeem it – but you’re probably very close!<br> <br> Once you’ve chosen your item, you’ll be able to specify how many you wish to receive through ticking the available check box.<br> <br> You can also click on ‘Go to Shop’ to view the complete list of merchandize that can be bought with Gold Tokens.<br> <br> After you click on the ‘Redeem’ button, a message will appear with the list of items you redeemed.</p></div> </div></div>   </div>                  </div>             </div>                              </div></div> <div class="title">        <div class="title-component">     <h2 class="h2 text-left                 primary-title">         Enjoy the club!     </h2> </div> </div> <div class="cta">           <div onmousedown="return false;" onselectstart="return false;" class="cta-component d-flex justify-content-start pt-medium">                     <div class="cta-template cta-secondary">         <a href="/openclient/" aria-label="Play Now!">                 <span class="label bold">Play Now!</span>                          </a>     </div>  </div></div> <div class="rich-text">            <div class="rich-text-component pt-xlarge">     <div class="text"><p><a href="/terms/888poker-club-tnc/">Terms &amp; Conditions</a></p></div> </div></div>               </div>      </div> </div></div>               </div>      </div> </div></div><?php include_once ($_SERVER["DOCUMENT_ROOT"]."/footer.php"); ?>